  "选 id 用 document.querySelector(\"#email\"),井号代表按 id 选。也可以用 getElementById(\"email\"),但 querySelector 更通用。": "Select by id with document.querySelector(\"#email\"); the hash means 'by id'. getElementById(\"email\") also works, but querySelector is more general.",
