  "校验从「拿到值」开始": "Validation starts by getting the value",
  "表单校验听起来很玄,其实第一步特别朴素:把用户输入的内容从页面里取出来。在 DOM 里,每个 <input> 都是一个元素对象,它当前显示的文字存在 .value 属性上。你先用 querySelector 找到这个元素,再读它的 .value,就拿到了「用户此刻敲进去的字」。": "Form validation sounds mysterious, but step one is humble: pull the user's text out of the page. In the DOM every <input> is an element object, and the text it currently shows lives on its .value property. Find the element with querySelector, read its .value, and you have exactly what the user typed right now.",
  "选中元素,再读它的 value": "Select the element, then read its value",
