  "trim() 是校验的隐形第一关": "trim() is the invisible first gate",
  "用户复制粘贴时常带上首尾空格,移动端输入法也爱在末尾塞个空格。如果不处理,「  」这种全是空格的输入会被你的「非空判断」放过去,后端再拒掉,体验很差。养成习惯:读出 value 后立刻 trim(),让「看起来空」的输入也真的算空。": "Users paste text with leading or trailing spaces, and mobile keyboards love to append one at the end. If you ignore that, an input of pure spaces sneaks past your 'non-empty' check and gets rejected later by the server — a poor experience. Make it a habit: trim() right after reading value so 'visually empty' input is truly empty.",
  "trim() 让首尾空格不再骗过校验": "trim() stops surrounding spaces from fooling the check",
