  "写 validateEmail(email):空字符串或不含 @ 时,把错误文字写进 #error 元素的 textContent 并返回 false;合法时清空错误并返回 true。": "Write validateEmail(email): when empty or missing @, set an error string on #error's textContent and return false; otherwise clear it and return true.",
  "判空最直接:if (email === \"\") 或 if (!email)。前面已经 trim() 过,所以纯空格也会落进这里。": "Check emptiness simply: if (email === \"\") or if (!email). Since you trimmed earlier, pure spaces land here too.",
  "改页面文字用 .textContent,不要用 innerHTML——错误文案是纯文字,textContent 还能挡住意外的 HTML 注入。": "Change page text with .textContent, not innerHTML — an error message is plain text, and textContent also blocks accidental HTML injection.",
  "合法时记得把 errorEl.textContent 清成 \"\",否则上一次的错误会一直挂在页面上不消失。": "On success, reset errorEl.textContent to \"\", or the previous error stays stuck on the page forever.",
